  <span class="italic">π</span> &lt; 1 is the size of the climate disaster. Utility is denoted by 
  <span class="italic">U</span>, consumption by 
  <span class="italic">C</span>, the production function by 
  <span class="italic">A</span> times 
  <span class="italic">F</span> before and 
