     </div>
    </div>
    <span xlink:href="10640_2018_231_Article_IEq11.gif" class="inline-graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
   </div>
  </div> and the value function 
  <div id="IEq12" class="inline-formula">
   <div class="alternatives">
    <span id="M31" class="tex-math">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$ V^{A} (K,\pi ) $$\end{document}</span>
    <div id="M32" class="math">
