    </div>
    <span xlink:href="10640_2018_231_Article_IEq12.gif" class="inline-graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
   </div>
  </div> (see “Appendix 1”). Before the climate regime shift, the problem becomes a stochastic optimal control problem. However, because we have modelled uncertainty by means of a hazard rate, it can be transformed into a deterministic one (Clarke and Reed 
